Enjoy this 30 minute all-levels flow brought to you by @thebalancedbachelorette 🧘‍♀️ 

TBB provides everything you’ll need for a relaxing yoga class right to your hotel or Airbnb. All classes can be tailored to meet the needs and requests of your group. Hangover, or lack thereof 😉 

Heading to Scottsdale for your BACH? You can book a class with them on the BACH app!

Charcuterie is the vibe all fall for BACH parties 🎃🥂 PLUS how cute are these different variations? We’re predicting these are going to be a HUGE hit this fall for parties!

Between the traditional cheese selection, breakfast spread, and dessert boards, the options are truly endless - and hard to pass up! Which one would you want for your BACH party? 🧀

node.text:
🎉 $2,000 GIVEAWAY 🎉 Whoa, this is a big one thanks to our friends at @viatortravel! We’re teaming up to hand one lucky winner $1,000 from each brand to spend on the perfect BACH trip and the honeymoon they’ve always dreamed of.  🏖️ Book exciting experiences using our app for your party before the big day, then hop over to Viator to book unforgettable honeymoon festivities for you and your newlywed boo.

Here’s all you have to do to enter:
1️⃣ Follow @thebachparty and @viatortravel
2️⃣ Like this post
3️⃣ Tag your friends in the comments below; each friend counts as an entry!
⭐ 2 bonus entries when you share to Stories and tag both brands

That’s it! 👯‍♀️ Not getting married but want to give your bestie the ultimate BACH party and honeymoon? We’ll transfer the prize to the bride or groom-to-be of your choice! So get sharing y’all 🎉

*Must be 18 or older and a US resident to participate in this giveaway. This giveaway is not sponsored, endorsed, or administered by, or associated with Instagram. ⁠By entering, entrants confirm they are 18+ years of age. This giveaway ends on FRI 9/17/2021 11:59 pm PST. Winner will be notified via Instagram direct message. Prize will be in the form of gift cards or promotional codes.

node.text:
POV: You’re living your best life with your best friends, celebrating your BACH party, on a yacht in Cabo 🍹 (talk about GOALS @kasia_mazi) ❤️

As we get closer to spooky season in the states, here are some ways to get the MOST out of Fall BACH parties:

🛥 Head to places like Cancun, Cabo, Scottsdale, Austin, or Miami where the weather is much better in fall than it is in the peak of summer

🎃 Lean into spooky season and have some fall themed festivities (think wine tasting, picnics, and movie nights)

📲 Download the BACH app to plan your perfect party

#bacheloretteparties #cabobachelorette #fallbachelorette #bridetobe #engaged #maidofhonor #destinationparty
